    Place
    Google Place returned from a Places method.
    Place.Address
    All address components in separate properties.
    Place.Id
    Unique identifier that can be used to retrieve details about a place.
    Place.Id.Filter
    Base class for Predicates that filter on place IDs.
    Place.IdFilter
    Search filter on place IDs.
    Place.OpeningHours
    Opening and closing times for a day (or span of days) on which a place is open.
    Place.Photo
    Photo for a place that can be downloaded by supplying the reference to Places.photo(Params).
    Place.Prediction
    Place or query that was returned from a Places autocomplete method.
    Place.Prediction.IdFilter
    Autocomplete filter on place IDs.
    Place.Review

    Place.Review.Aspect
